## Title of proposal: 
ENS Frontend 

## Description: 
Create an IPFS content hash of the frontend of syntehtix.exchange and Mintr and host it using an ENS domain name (see uniswapexchange.eth, uniswapexchange.eth.link)

## Motivation: 
The purpose of this proposal would be to create a persistant web3 version of the frontends to make them accessable to anyone, anywhere

## Additional information: 
ENS names with IPFS content hashes are available with web3 browsers like Metamask and Opera Beta, adding .link/ makes them accessable with any browser

## Previous work: 
uniswap.geoblock.eth uniswap.geoblock.eth.link uniswapexchange.eth Uniswapexchange.eth.link  tornado.geoblock.eth tornado.geoblock.eth.link 

